<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>GodLawBot | The Sovereign Source Protocol</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary-gold: #d4af37;
            --deep-black: #0a0a0a;
            --soft-white: #f4f4f4;
            --neon-blue: #00f2ff;
        }

        body {
            background-color: var(--deep-black);
            color: var(--soft-white);
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            padding: 20px;
            border: 1px solid var(--primary-gold);
            border-radius: 15px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.2);
        }

        h1 {
            color: var(--primary-gold);
            font-size: 3rem;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 5px;
        }

        .status-pulse {
            display: inline-block;
            width: 12px;
            height: 12px;
            background-color: var(--neon-blue);
            border-radius: 50%;
            margin-right: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px var(--neon-blue);
            animation: pulse 2s infinite;
        }

        @keyframes pulse {
            0% { transform: scale(0.95); box-shadow: 0 0 0 0 rgba(0, 242, 255, 0.7); }
            70% { transform: scale(1); box-shadow: 0 0 0 10px rgba(0, 242, 255, 0); }
            100% { transform: scale(0.95); box-shadow: 0 0 0 0 rgba(0, 242, 255, 0); }
        }

        .tagline {
            font-style: italic;
            color: #888;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .btn {
            background-color: var(--primary-gold);
            color: var(--deep-black);
            padding: 15px 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
            border-radius: 5px;
            transition: 0.3s;
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .btn:hover {
            background-color: var(--soft-white);
            transform: translateY(-3px);
        }

        .footer-note {
            margin-top: 50px;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            color: #444;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="container">
        <h1>GodLawBot</h1>
        <p><span class="status-pulse"></span> SYSTEM STATUS: BRAIN ACTIVE</p>
        <p class="tagline">Level 0 BIOS | The Sovereign Source Protocol</p>
        
        <p>Advanced autonomous logic and legal-tech integration. <br> 
        Bridging the gap between raw data and actionable intelligence.</p>

        <a href="https://github.com/your-username/godlawbot" class="btn">VIEW REPOSITORY</a>

        <div class="footer-note">
            Archived and Managed under Project MN-100
        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>

